quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  74,1,"E, mmwe ŵan'diunichile nguwo"
  74,2,Jimani ni mwaatetele (ŵandu)
  74,3,Soni Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) mwakusyaani
  74,4,Soni nguwo syenu siswejesyani
  74,5,Soni yakusakala (mpela isanamu) iŵambalani
  74,6,Soni ngasimumpa (jwinejwakwe chindu) ni ligongo lyakuti mpochele yejinji
  74,7,Soni ligongo lya Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) pililani
  74,8,Basi ndema jalichigombedwa lipenga
  74,9,Lyele lisikulyotu lichiŵa lisiku lyakunonopa kusyene
  74,10,Kwa achimakafili ngasiliŵa lyakwepepala
  74,11,Munekaani ni mundu jwanan'gumbile jikajikape
  74,12,Ninampele ipanje yejinji
  74,13,Ni ŵanache ŵakuŵanajo
  74,14,Ni nankolochesye (ndamo jakwe) kunkolochesya kwambone nnope
  74,15,Panyuma pakwe jukolaga tama janti ndili nan'jonjechesye
  74,16,Kwapi! Chisimu jwalakwejo jwaliji nkugakanila maaya Getu
  74,17,Chingankanganichisye ku ilagasyo yakusausya kuikwela
  74,18,Chisimu jwalakwe jwachetelele (yatajile paajigamba Qur’an) ni jwapimiile
  74,19,"Basi julwesedwe, ana jwapimiile chantiuli"
  74,20,"Soni julwesedwe, ana jwapimiile chantiuli"
  74,21,Kaneka ni jwalolite (ŵandu)
  74,22,Kaneko ni jwautile sinya ni kusakasya kungope (kulosya ukali)
  74,23,Kaneko soni jwachitundumalile (chikulupi) ni kulikwesya
  74,24,"Ni jwatite: “Nganijiŵatu jalakwe (Qur’aniji) ikaŵeje usaŵi waukupocheledwa (kuumila kwa asaŵi ŵakala).”"
  74,25,“Nganijiŵatu jalakwe (Qur’aniji) ikaŵeje maloŵe ga mundu.”
  74,26,Sampano tinan'jinjisye ku Saqara
  74,27,Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya Saqara
  74,28,(Weletu ni Moto) wangasigasya (chilichose chachiponyedwemo) soni wangachileka (kuti chikopoche)
  74,29,Wakutinisya ni kuŵiilisya lipende
  74,30,Pa walakweo pana (Achimalika ŵakuugosa) ŵakwana likumi kwisa nsano nancheche
  74,31,"Ni nganitwaaŵiika akuuloleela Moto ikaŵeje Achimalaika, soni nganituchiŵiika chiŵalanjilo chaocho ikaŵeje kuŵa mayeso gakwalinjila achimakafili, kuti asimichisye ŵandu ŵaŵapedwile chitabu (ya chiŵalanjilochi), ni kuti soni ajonjechesye chikulupi chao ŵandu ŵaakulupilile, soni kuti akakaichila ŵandu ŵaŵapedwile chitabu ni ŵakulupilila, ni kuti soni aŵala ŵamuli m’mitima mwao mwana ulwele (wa unakunaku) ni achimakafili ajileje: “Ana Allah akusaka chichi pachilandanyo chalakwechi?” Iyyoyopeyo niyaakutiji Allah pa kunnechelela kusokonechela jwansachile ni kun'jongola jwansachile. Ni pangali ŵaakumanyilila mikutula ja asilikali ŵa Ambuje ŵenu ikaŵeje Jwelepejo. Ni nganiuŵa Walakwe (Motowo) ikaŵeje chikumbusyo kwa ŵandu (cha kwatetela nacho)"